body: I am a software engineer working at [Looksee](http://www.havealooksee.com/). I have [worked](http://www.linkedin.com/in/walterblaurock) for [Next Big Sound](https://www.nextbigsound.com), Microsoft, and Apple, and received a B.S. in Computer Science from Brown University. In my spare time I enjoying taking [photos](http://instagram.com/walterblaurock) and writing [code](http://github.com/wb). You can find me on [facebook](http://facebook.com/walterblaurock) and [twitter](https://twitter.com/walterblaurock).
